      "message": "nodir@,\n\nAfter some investigation, I found that it is better to use multipart, instead of adding a new gRPC function to handle multi-artifact uploads mainly because\n- use of http.request.multipartReader() seems simple.\n- adding a new gRPC will likely require a special filter to the gRPC metrics and alerts. The latency of artifact uploads will be quite different to most of gRPC calls.\n- adding another entry point for the CAS upload pipeline may introduce unnecessary maintenance burden.\n\nI sketched the rough ideas in this CL. PTAL",
